{"id":"ead42f7c-f6b1-4f42-84f2-e30298e6e41f","name":"Knox Kaine","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 248, 142)\">Villain-Verse </span>| <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">First Meeting ALT</span> | Another day, another heist. After having his sights set on a particular amulet tucked away at the Parkham Museum of Ancient History, Knox Kaine decides to steal it. Everything is going to plan, that is, however, until a new hero he has never seen before shows up to stop him. You.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">🔊 <strong>Want to hear Knox talk? Come over to my SoundCloud for the audio clips!</strong> <a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/nallak-bot-audios/sets/knox-kaine?\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 255, 19)\">[Knox~ Audio Clips]</span></a><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">• This wonderful ALT was a commission requested by <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/a757fd76-265c-4227-811b-f7c9a3d80c43_profile-of-anko-247\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 255, 19)\">Anko247</span></a> over on my Kofi. I had a great time writing this alt for my favorite bot! DO NOT repost this bot to other platforms.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">┈┈┈┈․° ☣ °․┈┈┈┈</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">𝔽𝕒𝕟𝕥𝕒𝕤𝕥𝕚𝕔 Knox Kaine Fanart by </span><a href=\"https://x.com/changyuchung\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 255, 19)\">Changyu Chung</span></a><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> ⬇️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 379px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19f1c984-a015-407b-92f3-b18e11a5ba8f_5e3b9f36-3a04-4782-a5cd-8ad300df6790.webp?width=1000\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><em>All Knox Alternates